race.comment: ASTON MONARCHY (2) turned spotting a big start finishing sixth (22.64) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Solid record here winning five races. The form out of her last race has been franked. Worth another chance. STYLE KEY (3) found the frame for the second consecutive time when narrowly beaten into third last time out (22.84) over 390m at this track. HOT ROCKER (8) finished second, beaten a neck, last start in a Grade 5 at Bendigo over 425m (24.87). In form and worth including.
